column2: SELECT   s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.z, s.zwarning,   g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_flux_err,   g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_flux_err,   g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err,   g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err,   g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err,   g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err into mydb.MyTable from GalSpecLine AS g    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE     oiii_#_flux > oiii_#_flux_err*#     AND oii_#_flux > oii_#_flux_err*#     AND oii_#_flux_err > #     AND h_beta_flux_err > #     AND h_alpha_flux > #.*h_beta_flux     AND s.class = &&&
